In investigation found wile creating the credentials for Gmail and Drive we are opening the stream but not closing it.  Code:   @Override
  public GoogleAuthorizationCodeFlow buildInvoicingCodeFlow(InvoiceEmail account) throws IOException {
    InputStream secretFile = getResourceAsStream("/client_secret.json");
    String credentialsPath = ".credentials/" + account.getEmailId();
    GoogleClientSecrets clientSecrets = GoogleClientSecrets
        .load(JSON_FACTORY, new InputStreamReader(secretFile));
    return new GoogleAuthorizationCodeFlow
        .Builder(netHttpTransport, JSON_FACTORY, clientSecrets, SCOPES)
        .setDataStoreFactory(buildCredentialStoreFactory(credentialsPath))
        .setApprovalPrompt(AUTH_APPROVAL_PROMPT)
        .setAccessType(AUTH_ACCESS_TYPE)
        .addRefreshListener(buildCredentialRefreshListener(account))
        .build();
  } Expected Result: The stream should be closed after its scope is completed.

